{"tid":2282351,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"九陰真經 台服新服「斗轉星移」","createTime":"2020-11-11T22:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T16:31:33.000Z","uid":201992,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5c6dc0979bfcf4a8509f7fd2e98284e870435ab3","tid":2282351,"uid":201992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T22:13:43.000Z","msg":"是咁的咁啱留意到今個星期五台服開新服，講真玩左四年幾.但唔想玩大陸服（熱鬧但係全部都係支那仔），同埋呢個服我諗係呢個遊戲台服嘅最後一個服（香港，台，馬三個服已經合埋一齊）<br />\n睇吓可以召集到幾多有興趣巴打一齊玩，相信每個玩過嘅都有一個大俠夢. <br />\n<br />\n依家遊戲情況<br />\n以前八大門派，依家十一門派<br />\n以前玉裝一件幾百，依家幾百齊裝<br />\n其他諗到再講<br />\n<br />\n最後想講嘅係，呢個遊戲好玩嘅係同一齊玩嘅人.好多人都係抱住個心態多人玩先加入，如果冇第一個你點會有第二個佢。希望有興趣嘅可以一齊完呢個大俠夢<br />\n<br />\nTG谷Link: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/McRE0h1fxIw1h0CDrV0eTQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMcRE0h1fxIw1h0CDrV0eTQ&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=9ec50258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/McRE0h1fxIw1h0CDrV0eTQ</a><br />\n<br />\nDiscord:今晚會開<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JPyAd7g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJPyAd7g.jpg&h=29ed733a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8fa2ee7f593a0e4f8e3a53f062f02b6cb79253b2","tid":2282351,"uid":201992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T22:14:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d579a48427a92f20a869383e5c8b9df6dc73dd","tid":2282351,"uid":201992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T22:15:31.000Z","msg":"推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0079834d8b785fd7eeb88c445b8dc50c33e45f20","tid":2282351,"uid":201992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T22:16:53.000Z","msg":"推一下"},{"pid":"6fc052d948abf023cc3e0c8ad93e64a9e4610cbd","tid":2282351,"uid":187569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T22:24:12.000Z","msg":"入左群，起身